---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy"
	description={`The privacy policy for ${SITE_TITLE}, covering cookies, Google AdSense and other third-party advertising, affiliate links, and external links.`}
	pubDate={new Date('June 18 2026')}
>
	<p>{SITE_TITLE} ("we", "us", or "this site") respects your privacy. This page explains what
		information is collected when you visit and how it is used.</p>

	<h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
	<p>You can read everything on this site without creating an account, and we do not actively collect
		personally identifying information such as your name or contact details. However, cookies and
		standard access logs (browser type, pages visited, etc.) may be collected automatically for
		analytics and advertising purposes.</p>

	<h2>2. Cookies</h2>
	<p>This site uses cookies to improve your experience and to serve advertising. You can refuse or
		delete cookies in your browser settings, though some features may not work correctly if you do.</p>

	<h2>3. Google AdSense and third-party advertising</h2>
	<p>This site may display advertising from Google AdSense and other third-party vendors. These
		vendors, including Google, use cookies (such as the DoubleClick cookie) to serve ads based on
		your prior visits to this and other websites.</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your
			visits to this site and other sites on the internet.</li>
		<li>You can opt out of personalized advertising via <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.</li>
		<li>For how third-party vendors use cookies, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's advertising policies</a>.</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>4. Affiliate links</h2>
	<p>Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you click one and sign up for or purchase a
		product, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This does not influence our
		reviews or recommendations.</p>

	<h2>5. External links</h2>
	<p>This site contains links to external websites for reference. We are not responsible for the
		privacy practices of those sites — please review their own policies.</p>

	<h2>6. Data protection</h2>
	<p>We take reasonable steps to keep automatically collected information from being improperly
		disclosed, and use it only for analytics and advertising purposes.</p>

	<h2>7. Changes to this policy</h2>
	<p>This privacy policy may be updated to reflect changes in law or in the service. Any changes will
		be posted on this page.</p>

	<p>If you have any questions, please get in touch through the site.</p>
</Layout>
